sql:
SELECT name, level, experience
FROM characters
WHERE strength > (SELECT base_strength FROM classes WHERE class_name = 'Warrior') AND level >= 3;

external_knowledge:
- Skilled characters are those whose total attribute score (strength + agility + intelligence) exceeds 45;
- Challenging realms are those with a difficulty level greater than 2;
- Powerful attack abilities are those with a power greater than 10.

- The hierarchy level of a character is based on their level, with higher levels indicating a higher position in the hierarchy; 
- The average strength, agility, and intelligence for each character class are calculated across all characters in the class; 
- The average health and mana for each realm are calculated across all characters in the realm; 
- The cumulative experience for each realm is the sum of the experience of all characters in the realm, ordered by level; 
- The average level for each character class is calculated across all characters in the class.

sql:
SELECT name || ' (Level ' || level || ')' AS character_info
FROM characters
WHERE level = (SELECT MAX(level) FROM characters);
